---
import { Button } from 'astro-pure/user'
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import config from '@/site-config'

const meta = {
  title: 'Privacy Policy',
  description: 'Effective date: 2026-02-28'
}

const contact = (config as any).contact || {
  email: 'qiatao0305@163.com',
  website: 'https://your-website.com',
  region: 'China'
}
---

<PageLayout {meta}>
  <Button title='Back' href='/terms' variant='back' />
  <main class='mt-6 lg:mt-10'>
    <div id='content-header' class='animate'>
      <h1 class='mb-6 text-3xl font-medium'>Privacy Policy / 隐私政策</h1>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>Effective Date: February 28, 2026 / 生效日期：2026年2月28日</p>
    </div>

    <div id='content' class='animate mt-8 prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none'>
      <h2>Introduction / 介绍</h2>
      <p>This Privacy Policy describes how this personal blog ("we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, and protects your information when you visit our website.</p>
      <p>本隐私政策说明了本个人博客（"我们"、"我们的"或"本站"）在您访问我们的网站时如何收集、使用和保护您的信息。</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect / 我们收集的信息</h2>
      <h3>Automatically Collected Information / 自动收集的信息</h3>
      <p>When you visit this website, we may automatically collect certain information, including:</p>
      <p>当您访问本网站时，我们可能会自动收集某些信息，包括：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Browser Information</strong>: Browser type, version, and language / <strong>浏览器信息</strong>：浏览器类型、版本和语言</li>
        <li><strong>Device Information</strong>: Device type, operating system / <strong>设备信息</strong>：设备类型、操作系统</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Pages visited, time spent on pages, referring website / <strong>使用数据</strong>：访问的页面、页面停留时间、来源网站</li>
        <li><strong>IP Address</strong>: Your IP address (may be anonymized) / <strong>IP地址</strong>：您的IP地址（可能已匿名化）</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Information You Provide / 您提供的信息</h3>
      <p>If you choose to leave comments or contact us, you may provide:</p>
      <p>如果您选择留言或联系我们，您可能会提供：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name or username / 姓名或用户名</li>
        <li>Email address (if required for comments) / 电子邮件地址（如果评论需要）</li>
        <li>Comment content / 评论内容</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information / 我们如何使用您的信息</h2>
      <p>We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
      <p>我们使用收集的信息用于以下目的：</p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Website Operation</strong>: To provide and maintain our website / <strong>网站运营</strong>：提供和维护我们的网站</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong>: To understand how visitors use our website (if analytics tools are used) / <strong>分析</strong>：了解访问者如何使用我们的网站（如果使用分析工具）</li>
        <li><strong>Communication</strong>: To respond to your comments or inquiries / <strong>沟通</strong>：回复您的评论或询问</li>
        <li><strong>Security</strong>: To protect against unauthorized access or malicious activity / <strong>安全</strong>：防止未经授权的访问或恶意活动</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Third-Party Services / 第三方服务</h2>
      <p>This website may use third-party services that collect information:</p>
      <p>本网站可能使用收集信息的第三方服务：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Comment Systems</strong>: If we use a comment system (e.g., Waline, Giscus), they may collect information according to their own privacy policies / <strong>评论系统</strong>：如果我们使用评论系统（如 Waline、Giscus），它们可能根据各自的隐私政策收集信息</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong>: If we use analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics), they may collect usage data / <strong>分析工具</strong>：如果我们使用分析工具（如 Google Analytics），它们可能收集使用数据</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We encourage you to review the privacy policies of these third-party services.</p>
      <p>我们鼓励您查看这些第三方服务的隐私政策。</p>

      <h2>Cookies / Cookie</h2>
      <p>This website may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
      <p>本网站可能使用 Cookie 来改善您的浏览体验。您可以通过浏览器设置控制 Cookie。</p>

      <h2>Data Security / 数据安全</h2>
      <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>
      <p>我们实施合理的安全措施来保护您的信息。但是，通过互联网传输的方法都不是100%安全的。</p>

      <h2>Your Rights / 您的权利</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <p>您有权：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to your personal information / 请求访问您的个人信息</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information / 请求更正不准确的信息</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your information / 请求删除您的信息</li>
        <li>Object to processing of your information / 反对处理您的信息</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children's Privacy / 儿童隐私</h2>
      <p>This website is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
      <p>本网站不面向13岁以下的儿童。我们不会故意收集儿童的个人信息。</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy / 隐私政策的变更</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>
      <p>我们可能会不时更新本隐私政策。我们会在本页面发布新的隐私政策来通知您任何变更。</p>

      <h2>Contact Us / 联系我们</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
      <p>如果您对本隐私政策有任何疑问，请联系我们：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${contact.email}`}>{contact.email}</a> / 电子邮件：<a href={`mailto:${contact.email}`}>{contact.email}</a></li>
        <li>Website: <a href={contact.website} target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>{contact.website}</a> / 网站：<a href={contact.website} target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>{contact.website}</a></li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <p><em>This Privacy Policy was last updated on February 28, 2026. / 本隐私政策最后更新于2026年2月28日。</em></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</PageLayout>
